<p>You can witness Ripple&#8217;s global expansion through the establishment of international offices and operations, marking significant milestones in their journey. Ripple has formed strategic partnerships and collaborations with various organizations, including banking institutions, corporations, and cross-industry entities. These partnerships have been instrumental in expanding Ripple&#8217;s reach and building a strong global presence.</p>



