<p>As Ripple expands internationally, it&#8217;s crucial to discuss the strategic market entries and growth phases that have played a pivotal role in their global expansion. Ripple has achieved significant milestones through partnerships and collaborations in various sectors. These include banking partnerships, corporate collaborations, and cross-industry partnerships.</p>



